# Development Workflow Guide

## Setup and Dependencies
- Use Bun as the package manager and runtime
- Install dependencies using `bun install`
- Run development server with `bun dev`

## Code Organization
- Follow the component structure in [PLANNING.md](mdc:PLANNING.md)
- Keep components modular and reusable
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling
- Write semantic HTML with proper accessibility attributes

## Content Management
- Edit content in Markdown files within `src/content/`
- Use Astro's content collections for organization
- Keep content separate from presentation logic
- Document content structure changes in [PLANNING.md](mdc:PLANNING.md)

## Quality Assurance
- Test components across different screen sizes
- Ensure WCAG 2.1 AA compliance
- Validate Markdown content
- Check performance metrics
- Test interactive elements

## Version Control
- Use meaningful commit messages
- Create feature branches for new development
- Review code before merging to main
- Keep repository clean and organized
